quran[19{c,v,t}:
67,27,"phir jab yeh uss cheez ko qareeb dekh len ge to unn sab logon ke chehray baggar jayen ge jinhon ne inkaar kya hai, aur uss waqt un se kaha jaye ga ke yahi hai woh cheez jis ke liye tum takazey kar rahay thay"
67,28,"inn se kaho, kabhi tum ne yeh bhi socha ke Allah khuwa mujhe aur mere sathiyon ko halaak kar day ya hum par reham kere, kafiroon ko dard naak azaab se kon bacha le ga ?"
67,29,"inn se kaho, woh bara Raheem hai, isi par hum imaan laaye hain, aur usi par hamara bhrosa hai, anqareeb tumhe maloom ho jaye ga ke Sarih gumraahi mein para howa kon hai"
67,30,"inn se kaho, kabhi tum ne yeh bhi socha ke agar tumahray knoon ka pani zameen mein utar jaye to kon hai jo iss pani ki behti hui sotin tumhe nikaal kar laa day ga ?"
68,1,"noon, qasam hai qalam ki aur uss cheez ki jisay likhnay walay likh rahay hain"
68,2,tum apne rab ke fazl se majnu nahi ho
68,3,aur yaqeenan tumahray liye aisa ajar hai jis ka silsila kabhi khatam honay wala nahi
68,4,aur bay shak tum ikhlaq ke barray martabay par ho
68,5,anqareeb tum bhi dekh lau ge aur woh bhi dekh len ge
68,6,ke tum mein se kon junoon mein mubtala hai
68,7,"tumhara rab unn logon ko bhi khoob jaanta hai jo is ki raah se bhatkay hue hain, aur wohi un ko bhi achi terhan jaanta hai jo raah raast par hain"
68,8,lehaza tum inn jhutlanay walon ke dabao mein hargiz nah aao
68,9,yeh to chahtay hain ke kuch tum madahnat karo (dhelay parjaio_to yeh bhi madahnat karen
68,10,hargiz nah dabo kisi aisay shakhs se jo bohat kasmain khanay wala be waqat aadmi hai
68,11,"taanay deta hai, chughliyan khata phirta hai"
68,12,"bhalai se rokta hai, zulm o zayad-ti mein hadd se guzar jaane wala hai, sakht bad aamaal hai, jfaa car hai"
68,13,aur aَn sab ayob ke sath bad asal hai
68,14,iss bana par ke woh bohat maal o aulaad rakhta hai
68,15,jab hamari ayaat uss ko sunai jati hain to kehta hai yeh to aglay waqton ke afsaanay hain
